*
 * Create an STL File from a surface Object (e.g. for 3D printing)
 *
 * @example
 * molsurf = new MolecularSurface(structure)
 * surf = molsurf.getSurface({type: 'av', probeRadius: 1.4})
 * stl = new StlWriter(surf)
 * stl.download('myFileName')
